Looking towards Rodimus then looks back to Megatron Revived and then back to Rodimus.

&quot;I am Dracos, and indepentent faction that has gotten caught up with this planetsw struggles.&quot;

robert riley &lt;bustercross365@...&gt; wrote:
Megatron Revived:

&quot;No,&quot; the Emperor said,&quot; I fight for the Maximals.  I came to Earth of the Past to find my brother and sister.&quot;

A few minutes later they arived at Maximal base, Megatron slowed and landed, setting Dracos down befor ehe touched the ground.  Rodimus was already outside, he wanted to talk it seemed.

Jerame Johnson &lt;jeramej@...&gt; wrote:
Dracos:

&quot;Unicron, that name sound familure.&quot;

Dracos thinks for a minute, and begine to compile the rest of his memory core which is still intact.

&quot;Are you from the predicon Faction?&quot;

robert riley &lt;bustercross365@...&gt; wrote:
Megatron Revived:

&quot;I cannot tell you.  I have not been here long, but what I do know is that we have an ally in Unicron&#39;s control, and the cannon that was built has now been destroyed.  We are all recovering from that battle, everyone is wore out.  We will find our answers when we get to base and talk to Rodimus.&quot;

Jerame Johnson &lt;jeramej@...&gt; wrote:
Dracos:
&quot;Thank you and sorry for the troubles.&quot; Dracos looks at the land and starts  having memory core relapses.

&quot;This place seems so familure but I do not know where I am at, Could you fill me in? becouse all that I seem to remember is that I was exploring a cave and then a quake or something. I had to have been stuck there for a while.&quot;

robert riley &lt;bustercross365@...&gt; wrote:
Megatron Revived:

Megatron transformed and drifted down to Dracos.  It appeared Dracos was badly damaged.

&quot;At this rate, you will be offline before we get there.  I&#39;ll have to carry you the rest of the way,&quot; he said, beginning system checks on his vernier and other propulsion systems, carrying someone could strain his engines a little bit.

He landed and put his fusion cannon on it&#39;s latchings on his back and held on to Dracos under his arms as he lifted off the ground and started back to base again.  He quickly ramped up the speed, until they would get back to base in a few minutes.

Jerame Johnson &lt;jeramej@...&gt; wrote:
Dracos:
 Begins to follow Megatron in the direction of the base and begins running a system scan as well. Making a mental note that his transformation sequencer is completly Burned out and he has enough energy left to make it to the base. Dracos looks up to megatron and informs megatron &quot;My Transformation Sequencer is out of commision. And I am running on emergency energy and my internal sensor are dectecting a 5% energy depleation rate a minute. Umm I may need Emergency Field work within the next 2 hrs, How long will it be until we reach the destination point you are taking me to?&quot; 

Airly &lt;airly2002@...&gt; wrote:
Kup/Rodimus:

Rodimus had arrived a while ago with her little daughter in arm (who was giggling aloud) and replied &quot;Here&#39;s Rodimus... report if anything is out place... I like to chat with ya nd with the new comer&quot; and looking to Kup said &quot;Could you care Elita, since I go to attend the new commer, uncle Kup&quot;

Kup took the little baby and said &quot;Sur,e lad&quot;

Rodimus went towartds exit and waited to MEgatron and the new commer.
